---
import StandardPage from "../components/StandardPage.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<StandardPage 
  title="槳長計算器 | ACA 獨木舟手冊"
  badgeZh="裝備工具"
  badgeEn="Gear Tools"
  heroTitleMainZh="槳長計算器"
  heroTitleSubZh="算出你的專屬槳長"
  heroTitleMainEn="Paddle Length Calculator"
  heroTitleSubEn="Professional Biomechanical Fitting"
  descriptionZh="透過肘距、肌力與體重，精確計算出最符合您身體結構的槳長與握距。本工具基於 Michele Ramazza 的專業算法。"
  descriptionEn="Precisely calculate the ideal paddle length and grip width based on your biomechanics. Algorithm developed by Michele Ramazza."
  maxW="max-w-7xl" 
>
  <!-- Calculator Section -->
  <section id="calculator" class="mb-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <SectionHeader 
      titleZh="專業長度計算器"
      titleEn="Pro Length Calculator"
      descZh="請輸入精確數據以獲得最佳擬合結果。此計算器適用於溪流、旅遊、海洋與激流標桿。"
      descEn="Enter accurate data for optimal results. Valid for creek, touring, sea and slalom."
    />
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <!-- Input Form -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/20">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Elbow Distance -->
          <div>
            <label class="block mb-4">
              <span class="zh font-bold text-slate-800">1. 肘對肘距離 (cm)</span>
              <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight uppercase mt-1">Elbow to elbow distance</span>
            </label>
            
            <!-- Measurement Diagram (Hands-up Posture) -->
            <div class="md:bg-slate-50 md:rounded-2xl px-0 py-2 md:p-4 mb-6 flex justify-center md:border border-slate-100">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 200 110" class="w-full max-w-[240px] h-auto">
                <!-- Torso / Shoulders -->
                <path d="M82 60 Q100 55, 118 60 L125 100 L75 100 Z" fill="#cbd5e1" opacity="0.5" /> <!-- Torso -->
                <circle cx="100" cy="45" r="10" fill="#4796cc" /> <!-- Head -->
                
                <!-- Arms: Hands-up Posture -->
                <!-- Left Arm: Shoulder -> Elbow (Out) -> Hand (In) -->
                <path d="M85 62 L55 65 L75 40" fill="none" stroke="#4796cc" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                <circle cx="55" cy="65" r="3" fill="#fff" /> <!-- Elbow Apex -->
                
                <!-- Right Arm: Shoulder -> Elbow (Out) -> Hand (In) -->
                <path d="M115 62 L145 65 L125 40" fill="none" stroke="#4796cc" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                <circle cx="145" cy="65" r="3" fill="#fff" /> <!-- Elbow Apex -->
                
                <!-- Measurement Annotations -->
                <path d="M55 55 L145 55" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4" />
                <path d="M55 50 L55 60 M145 50 L145 60" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="2" />
                <path d="M55 55 L61 52 M55 55 L61 58 M145 55 L139 52 M145 55 L139 58" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="1.5" />
                
                <text x="100" y="25" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" font-weight="bold" fill="#f43f5e" class="uppercase tracking-widest">Measure Between Elbows</text>
              </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <input 
                type="number" 
                id="input-elbow" 
                value="95" 
                min="50" max="150"
                class="w-full bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-xl font-black text-blue-600 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-100 transition-all outline-none"
              />
              <span class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-300 font-bold">CM</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-3 italic">
              <span class="zh">雙臂平伸，測量兩肘尖之間的最長距離。</span>
              <span class="en">Measure from elbow to elbow with arms extended.</span>
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pull-ups -->
          <div>
            <label class="block mb-4">
              <span class="zh font-bold text-slate-800">2. 引體向上次數 (肌力指標)</span>
              <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight uppercase mt-1">Tractions on the bar</span>
            </label>

            <select 
              id="input-power"
              class="w-full bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-700 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-100 transition-all outline-none appearance-none"
            >
              <option value="0">無法完成或 1 次 (0-1)</option>
              <option value="1">1 到 5 次 (1-5)</option>
              <option value="5">5 到 10 次 (5-10)</option>
              <option value="10">10 次以上 (10+)</option>
              <option value="20">20 次以上 (20+)</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <!-- Weight -->
          <div>
            <label class="block mb-4">
              <span class="zh font-bold text-slate-800">體重 (kg)</span>
              <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight uppercase mt-1">Paddler weight (kg)</span>
            </label>
            <div class="relative">
              <input 
                type="number" 
                id="input-weight" 
                value="75" 
                min="20" max="200"
                class="w-full bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-xl font-black text-slate-700 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-100 transition-all outline-none"
              />
              <span class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-300 font-bold">KG</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Results Display -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-slate-900 rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-12 text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <!-- Abstract Decoration -->
        <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -left-20 -bottom-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-12">
          <!-- Result Visual Diagram -->
          <div class="md:bg-white/5 md:rounded-3xl px-0 py-4 md:p-6 md:border border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 300 120" class="w-full max-w-[400px] h-auto">
              <!-- Paddle -->
              <rect x="30" y="58" width="240" height="4" rx="2" fill="#475569" />
              <!-- Blades (Hidden on mobile to save space) -->
              <ellipse cx="30" cy="60" rx="25" ry="12" fill="#475569" opacity="0.6" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="0.5" class="hidden md:block" />
              <ellipse cx="270" cy="60" rx="25" ry="12" fill="#475569" opacity="0.6" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="0.5" class="hidden md:block" />
              
              <!-- Paddler Top Down -->
              <circle cx="150" cy="75" r="12" fill="#4796cc" /> <!-- Head -->
              <!-- Arms (Visualizing 45 degree angle) -->
              <path d="M138 75 Q110 75, 100 60" fill="none" stroke="#4796cc" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M162 75 Q190 75, 200 60" fill="none" stroke="#4796cc" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" />
              
              <!-- Annotations -->
              <!-- Grip Width -->
              <path d="M100 50 L200 50" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5" />
              <path d="M100 45 L100 55 M200 45 L200 55" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5" />
              <text x="150" y="42" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#fbbf24" font-weight="bold">GRIP WIDTH</text>
              
              <!-- Total Length -->
              <path d="M5 105 L295 105" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
              <path d="M5 100 L5 110 M295 100 L295 110" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
              <text x="150" y="115" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="#94a3b8" font-weight="bold">TOTAL LENGTH</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-blue-400 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Recommended Fitting</h4>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
              <!-- Total Length -->
              <div class="flex-1">
                <p class="zh text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1">建議槳總長</p>
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span id="result-total" class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white tabular-nums">195.7</span>
                  <span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-500">CM</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Grip Width -->
              <div class="flex-1 border-l border-slate-800 pl-8">
                <p class="zh text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1">建議內部握距</p>
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span id="result-grip" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-blue-400 tabular-nums">62.5</span>
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-500">CM</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Extra Advice -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
            <div>
              <p class="zh text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mb-2">Blade Surface</p>
              <p id="result-blade" class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Medium-Large</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Science & Logic Section -->
  <section id="science-logic" class="mb-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <SectionHeader 
      titleZh="槳長的科學與邏輯"
      titleEn="The Science of Paddle Length"
      descZh="為什麼生物力學指標比身高更重要？"
      descEn="Why biomechanical metrics trump height-based formulas."
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- 1. Height Myth -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <span class="zh">1. 破解「身高決定論」的迷思</span>
          <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight mt-1">Breaking the Height Myth</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="zh text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          傳統上，許多人習慣依照身高來選擇槳長，但這在生物力學上是存在缺陷的。獨木舟是一項<strong>「坐姿」</strong>運動，決定你划幅與力矩的關鍵在於你的<strong>軀幹高度 (Torso Height)</strong>、<strong>臂長 (Arm Span)</strong> 以及<strong>肩膀寬度</strong>。兩位身高相同的人，可能因為軀幹、臂展比例不同，而需要完全不同的槳長。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Power Triangle -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <span class="zh">2. 核心邏輯：動力三角形</span>
          <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight mt-1">The Power Triangle</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="zh text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          本工具的核心，是幫你找出身體發力最穩定、最安全的區間。有好的握距才能找到對的長度。
        </p>
        <ul class="zh space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>肘距 vs. 握距：</strong> 我們不參考肩膀寬度，而是測量具備功能性的「肘對肘距離」。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>0.658 黃金比例：</strong> 計算器輸出的握距，旨在讓你握槳時，肩膀自然處於最穩定的「肩胛面 (Scapular Plane)」。</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Verification & Angle Analysis -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-[2rem] px-4 py-8 lg:p-10 text-white lg:col-span-2 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-8 lg:mb-10 text-center">
          <span class="zh">3. 驗證你的理想握距</span>
          <span class="en text-xs text-blue-300 block tracking-tight mt-1">Grip Verification & Angle Analysis</span>
        </h4>

        <!-- Step 1: How to do it -->
        <div class="lg:bg-white/10 lg:p-8 lg:rounded-3xl lg:border lg:border-white/20 mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Diagram Container -->
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 lg:bg-white/5 lg:rounded-2xl px-0 py-2 lg:p-6 flex flex-col items-center lg:border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-blue-400 tracking-widest mb-6">Shoulder Angle Diagram (Top-down)</div>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 240 180" class="w-full max-w-[340px] h-auto">
                <!-- Human Head & Shoulders -->
                <circle cx="60" cy="110" r="15" fill="#4796cc" opacity="0.2" /> <!-- Head -->
                <text x="60" y="113" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#4796cc" font-weight="bold" opacity="0.8">頭</text>
                <rect x="10" y="105" width="100" height="10" rx="5" fill="#cbd5e1" opacity="0.1" /> <!-- Shoulders -->
                
                <!-- Joint Center (Shifted Further Left) -->
                <circle cx="110" cy="110" r="8" fill="#3b82f6" /> <!-- Shoulder Joint Right -->
                <text x="110" y="135" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#60a5fa" font-weight="bold">肩關節 (Joint)</text>
                
                <!-- 0 Degree (Forward) -->
                <line x1="110" y1="110" x2="110" y2="20" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4" />
                <text x="110" y="12" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8" font-weight="bold">0° 正前方</text>
                
                <!-- 90 Degree (Side) -->
                <line x1="110" y1="110" x2="170" y2="110" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4" />
                <text x="170" y="125" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#f43f5e" font-weight="bold">90° 脫臼風險</text>
                
                <!-- 45 Degree (Golden Zone) -->
                <path d="M110 110 L155 65" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" /> <!-- Upper Arm (Humerus) -->
                <path d="M110 90 A20 20 0 0 1 124.14 95.86" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3" />
                
                <text x="165" y="55" text-anchor="start" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-weight="black">45° 最佳角度</text>
                <text x="165" y="67" text-anchor="start" font-size="7" fill="#60a5fa" class="uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter">Optimal Angle</text>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-6 zh text-center">本圖呈現上臂相對於軀幹的夾角。藍色 45° 為力量與安全的最佳平衡點。</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Content Area -->
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="text-blue-400 font-black">● 俯瞰視角</div>
                    <p class="zh text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">想像從頭頂向下看你的雙臂位置。</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="text-blue-400 font-black">● 設定角度</div>
                    <p class="zh text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">將手肘從身體正前方向兩側張開至 <strong>45 度</strong>。</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 bg-blue-600/20 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/30">
                  <div class="text-blue-400 font-black mb-2">● 鎖定夾角 (最佳槓桿輸出)</div>
                  <p class="zh text-sm text-slate-200 leading-relaxed">
                    當肘關節呈現 90 度時，肱二頭肌與肱橈肌處於最佳的「長度-張力關係」，能最有效地將<strong>背闊肌、胸大肌</strong>產生的力量，透過前臂這根槓桿，毫無損失地傳遞到槳桿上。
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <div class="text-blue-400 font-black">● 得出寬度</div>
                  <p class="zh text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">此時雙手間距離，即為你發力最穩定、最保護肩膀的參考握距。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="space-y-3 p-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl shadow-xl order-first">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white">45°</div>
            <p class="zh text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
              <strong>最佳角度：</strong> 這是肩膀最穩定、肌群發力最平衡的角度（肩胛面）。在受力時，肩膀的負擔最輕。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-500">0°</div>
            <p class="zh text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
              雖然安全但力矩太短，無法透過核心旋轉發力，容易變成低效的「推槳」。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3 p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-red-500">90°</div>
            <p class="zh text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
              傳統 90 度規則。會讓肩關節處於外展與外旋極限，受力時極易導致擠壓或脫臼。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Balance -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-10 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <span class="zh">4. 長度與力量的平衡</span>
          <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight mt-1">Power & Cadence Balance</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="zh text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          最後，計算器會根據你的<strong>肌力 (引體向上次數)</strong> 與<strong>體重</strong>微調總長度：
        </p>
        <ul class="zh space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>強壯的划者：</strong> 可以支撐更長的力臂（較長的槳），以換取更高的單槳推力。</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>重視頻率的划者：</strong> 較短的槳能提升划頻 (Cadence)，並減輕關節在長途巡航時的負擔。</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Torso & Seat Height -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-10 border border-slate-200">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <span class="zh">補充：關於坐高與軀幹</span>
          <span class="en text-xs text-slate-400 block tracking-tight mt-1">Seat Height & Torso Note</span>
        </h4>
        <p class="zh text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          取得握距後，下一步即是計算「抓握點到槳葉」的距離。這段距離理論上取決於<strong>軀幹長度</strong>與<strong>船型坐高</strong>。
        </p>
        <p class="zh text-slate-500 text-sm italic">
          由於坐高在大多數船型中是可以輕易調整的（如墊高塊），每艘船吃水深度不同，因此不將其列入計算器的固定參考。建議以計算器得出的長度為基準，再依個人習慣坐高、船型微調。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hand Distance Guide Section -->
  <section id="hand-distance" class="mb-24 scroll-mt-32">
    <SectionHeader 
      titleZh="握距標定指南"
      titleEn="Hand Distance Guide"
      descZh="如何將計算出的理想握距應用到你的槳桿上？"
      descEn="How to apply the calculated grip width to your paddle shaft."
    />

    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-[2rem] p-6 lg:p-12 border border-slate-200 shadow-inner">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
          <p class="zh text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            透過計算器得出理想握距後，你可以使用<strong>絕緣膠帶</strong>在槳桿上纏繞數圈作為參考點。
          </p>
          <ul class="zh space-y-4 text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-1">1</span>
              <span>找出槳桿的精確中心點。</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-1">2</span>
              <span>以此中心點為準，對稱地向左右標示出計算出的距離值。</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-1">3</span>
